Disco Mod
di_mustgr_dre
This Mod is made just to have a rest. Main Idea is to dance by music in Disco Room. But if you are bored you could go to Bunny Hop or Knife Arena. By passing BH you could receive grenade which will increase your movement speed. There are also 4 grenade-lasers (2 in toilet, 1 in garage, 1 in owner office).
Disco PlayList:
Mustgrr - Duty Calls Dr.Dre feat. Cosby - Studged
Map Features
- Cubemaps - Optimised Map (Nodraw, Hint\Skip) - Good Design (Nice Textures and Props). Such Design Elements like - Barmen, Guards, Dancers
Current Map Version is 0.2.1
